  <section class="overview">
    <h2>Overview</h2>
    <p>Led the development of Devex's first comprehensive design system, creating a unified visual language and component library that improved consistency and development efficiency across all digital products.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="challenge">
    <h2>The Challenge</h2>
    <p>Devex's digital products were experiencing inconsistencies in design and development, leading to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Inconsistent user experiences across different sections of the platform</li>
      <li>Redundant development work for similar components</li>
      <li>Difficulty in maintaining brand consistency</li>
      <li>Slower development cycles due to lack of reusable components</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="solution">
    <h2>The Solution</h2>
    <p>Developed a comprehensive design system that included:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Core design tokens for colors, typography, spacing, and breakpoints</li>
      <li>Component library with detailed documentation</li>
      <li>Usage guidelines and best practices</li>
      <li>Implementation examples and code snippets</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="impact">
    <h2>Impact</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Reduced development time by 40% for new features</li>
      <li>Improved design consistency across all products</li>
      <li>Streamlined onboarding for new team members</li>
      <li>Enhanced brand recognition and user trust</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
